6 3. Number of syringes, test kits and antagonists distributed;
7 4. Number of used syringes collected; and
8 5. Number of rapid HIV and viral hepatitis tests performed
9 including the number of reactive test results.
10 D. The State Commissioner of Health shall promulgate rules for
11 the implementation of this section.
12 SECTION 2. This act shall become effective November 1, 2025.
